
;奴隷受け取り地の文
@SLAVE_RECEIVE_MESSAGE

IF CFLAG:輪姦回数
	PRINTFORML Though %CALLNAME% is relieved to finally be freed from the assault, she realizes she isn't truly safe and start trembling in fear...
ELSEIF TALENT:無関心 || TALENT:感情乏しい
	PRINTFORML %CALLNAME% is staring back with an expressionless face...
ELSEIF TALENT:臆病 || TALENT:悲観的
	PRINTFORML %CALLNAME% is trembling in fear, wondering what will happen next...
ELSEIF TALENT:高慢 || TALENT:プライド高い
	PRINTFORML %CALLNAME% is screaming to be released immediately...
ELSE
	PRINTFORML When %CALLNAME% realizes %CALLNAME:0% is the ringleader, she glare back defiantly...
ENDIF




